# OptiQuery AI

OptiQuery AI is a production-grade Natural Language to SQL (NL-to-SQL) SaaS platform.

## Features
- Dynamic SQL Translation and query optimization
- Multi-database connections (PostgreSQL, MySQL)
- Interactive chatbot console and history
- Schema metadata harvesting and mapping
- Security auditing and access logging
